/target
# Cargo.lock IS committed — wolfstack is a binary, so the lockfile must be
# tracked for reproducible CI builds. Floating deps drifted `time` onto a
# version that broke `cookie` 0.16.2 on rustc 1.96 and failed the v24.39.0
# release; pinning prevents that class of failure.
*.swp
*.swo
*~
.idea/
.vscode/
.iso-build/
*.iso
